description:
The Beurer MG295 High Definition Shiatsu Massage seat cover features penetrating 3D deep massage relief, Shiatsu neck massage with electronic neck height adjustment, Spot Massage and soothing rolling massage for upper, lower and full back massage. The ergonomic bucket seat shape makes the MG295 comfortable for every body size and optional heat melts away muscle tightness and stress. Other features include heat in seat cushion, 2 Massage Speeds, Light and Heat Function, fully removable, washable neck mesh, washable, luxurious velour body covers, handy hook for convenient storage along with an easy to use remote control. The solid, comfortable back dimensions are 46 x 82cm with comfortable seat dimensions of 44 x 38cm. German Design. German Engineering.

Features:

  • Penetrating 3D deep massage relief
  • Electrically adjustable Height for shiatsu neck massage - built into remote
  • 3 massage types: Spot Massage, Soothing and Rolling massage
  • 3 Massage regions: Upper, Lower and Full Back Massage
  • Ergonomic and Comfortable 'Pod' Seat shape
  • In-Seat heating
  • 2 Massage Speeds
  • Light and Heat Function
  • Fully removable, washable neck mesh
  • Breathable mesh back cover - can be sponge cleaned for easy care
  • Handy hook for convenient storage
  • Easy to use remote control
  • Solid, comfortable back
  • Comfortable Seat


Specifications:

  • Model Number: MG 295
  • Dimensions:
    • Back: Approx 46 x 82cm
    • Seat: Approx 44 x 38cm
  • Function:
    • Penetrating 3D back massage
    • Spot massage
    • Soothing roll massage
  • Number of massage heads: 4
  • Cover: Yes
  • Timer: Yes
  • Wattage: 60 W
  • Warranty: 3 Year
